title: Brian Tracy: Fit and Trim for Life
description:
Brian Tracy: Fit and Trim for Life
MP3 @ 128 Kbps, 2 channels, 44.1 KHz | Duration: 73 Minutes | 70 MB
Genre: Audio CD in Self-help | Language: English

Learn how to get your weight under control and keep it there for life! Learn the secrets to being healthy and happy for life. Recapture the health, vitality and physique of your youth TODAY! In the 21st century, 30 is the new 20 and people are living longer and fuller lives. People are hitting their stride in their late 50's and aren't retiring at 65.

Don't you want to make the most of your life? Don't you want to be able to enjoy your retirement with boundless energy?

That is why you need to learn how to be Fit and Trim for Life.

In this 73-minute program, I'll explain how you can start leading a healthier lifestyle NOW. We all want to have the energy to play with our children or spend quality time with our spouse. We want to feel physically strong, slim and confident. And now you can.

After listening to this program and implementing my techniques you'll be able to ENJOY LIFE TO THE FULLEST and make the most out of every day you spend at work or with your children or spouse.
